name: Nairobi Blue
description:
Esù is the messenger of heavens.
Some say he has a lot of names, each one for the many faces he may present as: one day, a beautiful woman with a luscious body. The other, an old man rambling about life. Or maybe a child, playing tricks with you, waiting to see your reaction.
He's a mystical being, whose purpose is solely showing you the truth about yourself.
And keep this in mind - we all crossed paths with him one time or another, but he's just that good at disguising himself.
